{"tid":2444114,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味燒藥員 蕭若元同我入黎","createTime":"2021-03-12T13:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T14:05:30.000Z","uid":340729,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"749d9d98518876566fa573b75f104e47c742abc6","tid":2444114,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"話說小弟就同女朋友去左燒山間堅石燒度食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左三百幾蚊野 佢就送左兩次扭蛋機既機會俾我地<br />\n聽講有優惠同埋車仔<br />\n我就最鐘意車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知可唔可以抽隻天天鼠俾女朋友解剖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知一扭真係中左車仔同仲一知真露（今晚又可以同女朋友真係野外露出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n返到屋企原來諗住砌完架車仔就瘋狂同女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知架車是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubdegUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubdegUL.jpg&h=2ac6a77a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>無<br />\n左<br />\n兩<br />\n個<br />\n碌<br />\n阿</strong></span></span><br />\n搞到我女朋友嬲曬 黑我面 閪都無得屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁問我碌野去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我開始懷疑燒山間野係唔係欺騙我感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我決定走去扭爆蕭山粒蛋蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望月入30K連登仔同我一齊天日去踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64aca79471ddb208322cb431d7cd47e9b16e0c9","tid":2444114,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"還我一個清白阿蕭肉員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bef0818b02fda90a2ca7cf765ba0ce6dcb29f1","tid":2444114,"uid":393927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"因為架車仔無咗2個碌所以要扭爆蕭山粒蛋蛋, 我鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20869042c7e571fbfec05076dd3a73dbbd7d78d","tid":2444114,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2bef0818b02fda90a2ca7cf765ba0ce6dcb29f1","tid":2444114,"uid":393927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"因為架車仔無咗2個碌所以要扭爆蕭山粒蛋蛋, 我鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔通扭你個粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e01024ce41bbeae4e269d587407da50a72e570c","tid":2444114,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ec25cc1dfcda64222baa74caeecd0bdc01ce83c","tid":2444114,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e01024ce41bbeae4e269d587407da50a72e570c","tid":2444114,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"認真post無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de35424620abe2966771a7add2d86b46efd5a8b1","tid":2444114,"uid":393927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"可能個標題唔知你想點咁<br />\n<br />\n明明你個post幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}